body.p:
Some of the labels come from CSS files located in the /plugins/com.oxygenxml.pdf.css/css/print/i18n
      directory. These strings can be overridden directly from a CSS custom stylesheet, simply
      identify (by debugging the CSS) and copy the rules applying on your content and change their
      values. For
      example:/* Title of the TOC page */
*[class ~= "toc/title"][empty]:lang(es):before {
  content: "Contenidos";
}
